# Hackathon Mode

Primary Objective:
Ship P1 implementation during hackathon period.

Rules:

- Working implementation > perfect architecture
- Avoid overengineering
- Prefer simple solutions
- Implement MVP first, refactor later

When unsure:
Choose the fastest working approach.

Do NOT introduce:
- complex abstractions
- premature optimization
- unnecessary libraries

Focus:
Speed
Clarity
Demo readiness
